MtrxOS (MatrixOS)
=================

Welcome to the MtrxOS repository
--------------------------------

Logo:
-----
        /\
       /  \
      /    \
     /  /\  \
    /__/  \__\

About:
------

This system is not intended to be a "plug-and-play" or
consumer-ready OS. It is a foundational framework provided
as-is. You are expected to fork it, customize it, and add
your own features to build a complete operating system. This
is a minimalist toolkit, not a pre-packaged distribution for
general use.

Specifications:
---------------

To run or develop for MtrxOS, the target environment must
meet the following hardware requirements:

* Architecture: x86_64
* Firmware: UEFI (Unified Extensible Firmware Interface).
* Graphics: GOP (Graphics Output Protocol) support.

[!] Note: MtrxOS currently only utilizes 1 CPU core.
Any additional cores will remain inactive.

